Phn tch v Khm ph d liu.

Tm cu tr li cho cc cu hi nghin cu:

  • Nhng c trng v t kha no mang tnh phn bit cao nht trong mt tin tuyn dng gi mo.

M t d liu:

  • Job_id : id ca cng vic
  • title : tiu ca bi bo tuyn dng
  • location : a ch ca cng ty - ni lm vic
  • department : v tr cng vic
  • salary_range : Khong lng
  • company_profile : profile ca cng ty
  • description : M t
  • requirements : yu cu ca cng vic
  • benefits : quyn li
  • telecommuting : c s lin lc hay khng
  • has_company_logo : cng ty c logo hay khng
  • has_questions : c cu hi hay khng
  • employment_type : kiu cng vic (full-time, part-time, other)
  • required_experience : yu cu kinh nghim
  • required_education : yu cu hc v
  • industry : lnh vc cng vic
  • function : vai tr cng vic
  • fraudulent : gian ln hay khng

In[39]:
whilelist = []
for word in STOPWORDS:
    fake_mean = fake_text.str.count(fr'\b{re.escape(word)}\b').mean()
    real_mean = real_text.str.count(fr'\b{re.escape(word)}\b').mean()
    if fake_mean > real_mean:
        whilelist.append(word)
    else: continue

In[45]:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer

# --- BC 1: KIM TRA & SA LI D LIU ---
print("--- [DEBUG] Kim tra d liu ---")
print(f"Cc gi tr gc trong ct 'fraudulent': {df['fraudulent'].unique()}")

# 1. p kiu ct nhn v s nguyn (0 v 1)
# Nu ct ny ang l ch "1", "0" hoc float 1.0, 0.0 th lnh so snh == 1 s b sai
df['fraudulent'] = pd.to_numeric(df['fraudulent'], errors='coerce').fillna(0).astype(int)

# 2. Reset Index (CC K QUAN TRNG)
# Nu trc  bn  xa dng (drop), index b nhy cc (0, 2, 5...)
# iu ny lm cho vic khp gia DataFrame v Ma trn X b lch
df = df.reset_index(drop=True)

# 3. X l ct text (trnh li NaN)
df['combined_text'] = df['combined_text'].fillna("").astype(str)

print(f"S lng tin GI sau khi sa: {sum(df['fraudulent'] == 1)}")
print(f"S lng tin THT sau khi sa: {sum(df['fraudulent'] == 0)}")

# --- BC 2: TNH TON (Code chnh) ---
if sum(df['fraudulent'] == 1) == 0:
    print(" LI: Vn khng tm thy tin gi no. Hy kim tra li file d liu gc!")
else:
    # Vector ha
    vec = CountVectorizer(stop_words='english', max_features=5000)
    X = vec.fit_transform(df['combined_text'])
    feature_names = vec.get_feature_names_out()

    # To mask (Lc ny chc chn ng v  p kiu int)
    mask_fake = (df['fraudulent'] == 1).values
    mask_real = (df['fraudulent'] == 0).values

    # Tch ma trn
    X_fraud = X[mask_fake]
    X_real = X[mask_real]

    # Tnh tng
    fraud_counts = np.array(X_fraud.sum(axis=0)).flatten()
    real_counts = np.array(X_real.sum(axis=0)).flatten()

    # To bng kt qu
    df_freq = pd.DataFrame({
        'word': feature_names,
        'fraud_count': fraud_counts,
        'real_count': real_counts
    })

    # Tnh t l (Smoothing +1)
    df_freq['fraud_ratio'] = (df_freq['fraud_count'] + 1) / (df_freq['real_count'] + 1)

    # Lc kt qu (Ly t xut hin tng cng > 5 ln thi  m bo c kt qu)
    df_freq = df_freq[df_freq['fraud_count'] + df_freq['real_count'] > 5]

    print("\n THNH CNG! Di y l kt qu:")
    print("\n=== TOP 15 T C T L XUT HIN TRONG TIN GI CAO NHT ===")
    # y l nhng t "DU HIU LA O"
    print(df_freq.sort_values(by='fraud_ratio', ascending=False).head(15)[['word', 'fraud_count', 'real_count', 'fraud_ratio']])

    print("\n=== TOP 15 T PH BIN NHT TRONG TIN THT ===")
    print(df_freq.sort_values(by='real_count', ascending=False).head(15)[['word', 'real_count']])
